<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<style>
  body {
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    background-color: #111; 
    color: #069a2e; 
  }
  .container {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 20px;
  }
  .header {
    font-size: 24px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  .event-info {
    font-size: 16px;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .details {
    font-size: 14px;
    text-align: center;
  }
  @media screen and (min-width: 600px) {
    .container {
      flex-direction: row;
      justify-content: space-between;
    }
    .header {
      font-size: 32px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .event-info {
      font-size: 18px;
      text-align: left;
      margin-right: 20px;
    }
    .details {
      font-size: 16px;
      text-align: left;
    }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container">
  <div class="header">Eurovision</div>
  <div class="event-info">
    <p>Date: 09 may 2024 </p>
    <p>Venue: Malm√∂ Arena</p>
  </div>
  <div class="details">
    <p>Watch my video about the Eurovision song contest on youtube soon.</p>
    <p>You can see me waving ukrainian flag in the red circle on 2:12:08	https://youtu.be/NAEX4UX6HaQ!</p>
  </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>
